  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "In a bowl, mix together the shredded Monterey Jack cheese and sliced xtra sharp American cheese.",
    "Warm the corn tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by spooning the cheese mixture onto a tortilla and shaping like nigiri.",
    "Top each taco with chopped cilantro, scallions, and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro and scallions if desired."
